<script language="javascript" type="text/javascript">
    var TrySYVCoPopUp = false;

    function getTrySYVCoPopUp() {
        return TrySYVCoPopUp;
    }

    function setcuquie(total_clicks) {
        var today = new Date();
        today.setTime(today.getTime());
        var expires = 1 * 1000 * 60 * 60 * 24;
        var expires_date = new Date(today.getTime() + (expires));
        var clicks = parseInt(GetCookie());
        // alert( ' el vlaor qeu devuelve el get cliks es = '+ clicks);
        //alert( ' el vlaor que envio el totlas cliks es = '+ total_clicks);
        if (clicks < total_clicks) {
            // alert( ' el vlaor qeu devuelve el get cliks es = '+ clicks);
            clicks = total_clicks;
        } else {
            clicks = clicks + 1;
            //alert( ' el vlaor qeu devuelve el get cliks es = '+ clicks);
        }
        //            alert( ' el valor de cliks es = '+ clicks);
        var path = '/';
        var secure = '';
        //alert('creo patuh = ' + path);
        var domain = '';
        //alert('creo dominio = ' + domain);
        document.cookie = 'SUHregisterclicks=' + escape(clicks) +
            ((expires) ? ";expires=" + expires_date.toGMTString() : "") +
            ((path) ? ";path=" + path : "") +
            ((domain) ? ";domain=" + domain : "") +
            ((secure) ? ";secure" : "");
        //alert('el click es : ' + clicks);
        return clicks;

    }
    function GetCookie() {
        // cookies are separated by semicolons
        //      alert('todas la cokies son : ' + document.cookie);
        var aCookie = document.cookie.split("; ");
        for (var i = 0; i < aCookie.length; i++) {
            // a name/value pair (a crumb) is separated by an equal sign
            var aCrumb = aCookie[i].split("=");
            //        alert ('l odel cokier qeu evalua es : ' + aCrumb);
            //      alert ('lo final a evaluar es: ' + aCrumb[0]);
            if (aCrumb[0])
                if ('SUHregisterclicks' == aCrumb[0]) {
                var reg = aCrumb[1];
                //        alert('encotnro la co1 = ' + reg);
                if (reg == NaN) {
                    //          alert('encotnro el nana' );
                    reg = 0;
                }
                if (reg == 'NaN') {
                    //        alert('encotnro el nana' );
                    reg = 0;
                }
                //  alert('encotnro la co2 = ' + reg);
                return unescape(reg);
            }
        }
        // a cookie with the requested name does not exist
        return 0;
    }
    

 
   </script>

    function initsidebarmenu() {
        for (var i = 0; i < menuids.length; i++) {
            var ultags = document.getElementById(menuids[i]).getElementsByTagName("ul");
            for (var t = 0; t < ultags.length; t++) {

                    ultags[t].style.left = ultags[t - 1].getElementsByTagName("a")[0].offsetWidth + "px";  //position menu to the right of menu item that activated it
                ultags[t].parentNode.onmouseover = function() {
                    this.getElementsByTagName("ul")[0].style.display = "block";
                }
                ultags[t].parentNode.onmouseout = function() {
                    this.getElementsByTagName("ul")[0].style.display = "none";
                }
            }
            for (var t = ultags.length - 1; t > -1; t--) { //loop through all sub menus again, and use "display:none" to hide menus (to prevent possible page scrollbars
                ultags[t].style.visibility = "visible";
                ultags[t].style.display = "none";
            }
        }
    }

    if (window.addEventListener)
        window.addEventListener("load", initsidebarmenu, false);
    else if (window.attachEvent)
        window.attachEvent("onload", initsidebarmenu);

</script>
